sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Main as transpile core
    participant JsMain as js_main (JIT)
    participant Drain as js_event_loop_drain
    participant Uv as libuv uv_run
    participant Prep as uv_prepare / uv_check
    participant MQ as js_microtask_flush
    participant Timer as timer_fire_cb
    participant Fin as MIR_finish

    Main->>JsMain: call js_main(Context)
    JsMain-->>Main: completion value (sync body done)
    Main->>Drain: js_event_loop_drain()
    Drain->>MQ: flush nextTick + microtasks first
    Drain->>Uv: lambda_uv_run (UV_RUN_DEFAULT)
    loop until no active handles or watchdog 5000 ms
        Uv->>Prep: prepare_cb before poll
        Prep->>MQ: drain_task_checkpoint
        Uv->>Timer: fire due setTimeout/setInterval
        Timer->>JsMain: js_call_function(callback)
        Uv->>Prep: check_cb after poll
        Prep->>MQ: drain_task_checkpoint
    end
    Drain->>MQ: final flush after loop exits
    Drain-->>Main: return
    Note over Main: restore _lambda_rt AFTER drain
    Main->>Fin: MIR_finish (or defer for modules)
